description: ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund - ICICI Prudential Nifty Low Vol 30 iWIN ETF is an exchange traded fund co-launched by Prudential plc and ICICI Bank Ltd. It is managed by ICICI Prudential Asset Management Company Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets of India. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the low volatile stocks of large-cap companies. It seeks to replicate the performance of the Nifty 100 Low Volatility 30 Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund - ICICI Prudential Nifty Low Vol 30 iWIN ETF was formed on June 30, 2017 and is domiciled in India.
name: ICICI Prudential Nifty 100 Low Volatility 30 ETF
